➜杭州学渣没能毕业，却靠模仿大牌赚翻，被赞是后浪之光
http://www.sohu.com/a/416410031_157906	15456
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=213155279&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/4fa682ef13e64b3fa9cf9ad53c509a14.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>80后杭州小伙周轶伦，</p>
<p>念大学时，因为成绩太差没能毕业，</p>
<p>离开学校之后，</p>
<p>却用最便宜的材料，</p>
<p>做出了一件件爆款家具。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/0f117c9a17ca4f57ad5a1c7e7fdff4ee.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/c20b6615410b4d66a2741003246b2365.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
